sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Candidate
    actor HR
    participant Frontend as Vue/Inertia App
    participant Backend as Laravel API
    participant Storage as Cloudflare R2 / MinIO
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Reverb as Laravel Reverb
    
    %% Application Submission Phase
    Candidate->>Frontend: Browse Vacancies & Click Apply
    Candidate->>Frontend: Upload CV & Portfolio
    Frontend->>Backend: POST /api/v1/applications (Files attached)
    Backend->>Storage: Store Document Files
    Storage-->>Backend: Return Secure File URLs
    Backend->>DB: Save Application (Status: 'Screening')
    Backend->>Reverb: Broadcast 'NewApplication' Event
    Backend-->>Frontend: Return Success Response
    Reverb-->>HR: Push Real-time Notification
    Frontend-->>Candidate: Redirect to 'My Applications' Page
    
    %% HR Review Process
    HR->>Frontend: View Applicants & Open CV
    Frontend->>Storage: Fetch File from Storage
    Storage-->>Frontend: Serve Document
    HR->>Frontend: Change Status to 'Interview'
    Frontend->>Backend: PATCH /api/v1/applications/{id}/status
    Backend->>DB: Update Application Status
    Backend->>Reverb: Broadcast 'ApplicationStatusUpdated'
    Backend-->>Frontend: Acknowledge Update
    Reverb-->>Candidate: Push Real-time Notification
    
    %% Final Decision
    HR->>Frontend: Approve & Assign Mentor
    Frontend->>Backend: POST /api/v1/applications/{id}/approve
    Backend->>DB: Update Status to 'Accepted' & Link Mentor
    Backend->>Reverb: Broadcast 'ApplicationAccepted' Event
    Backend-->>Frontend: Success Confirmation
    Reverb-->>Candidate: Push Real-time "Accepted" Notification
